bolite caused concentration-dependent inhibition of platelet aggregation in vitro with IC50 of 5.5 µM and 0.21 µM, respectively. However, at clinically relevant concentrations, there was no effect on platelet aggregation test parameters following multiple dose administration of selexipag in healthy patients. ', 'DrugBank', 0, 0, 0);
